(firstQuint)Probiotics Effect on Glucose and Lipid Metabolism and Gut Microbiota in Patients With Obesity.

 This study aims to evaluate the effect of probiotics on the improvement of glucose and lipid metabolism, as well as the gut microbiota.

Baseline, 1 month and 3 months data will be collected and put into analysis to provide some suggestions on the probiotics use in the clinical practice for obesity patients.

